# Releases

This folder contains packaged releases (ZIP files with EXE).

Files:

- `releases.json` — log of all releases (version, date, size, test status)
- `ClientManager-vX.Y.Z-win64.zip` — release archives

These ZIP files are also published as [GitHub Releases](https://github.com/kscrewdze/client-management-system/releases).
